These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: magic-tricks, dancing
Job: accountant, project-manager
1. Job:accountant is in an even position##4
2. Job:project-manager == Hobby:dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | dancing | magic-tricks |
| Job     | project-manager    | accountant   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: water, tea
Sport: surfing, badminton
1. Sport:surfing is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:tea is on the left of Beverage:water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | tea | water        |
| Sport      | surfing  | badminton |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
